Lightning Cannon	TYPE:Siege Engine	COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:DMG	SPROP:AC 19, HP 30, Lightning Ball (Requires Aim). Ranged Attack Roll: +6, range 300/1,200 ft. Hit: 22 (4d10) Lightning damage.
